        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Clarifying Legality and Enforcement Action Reasoning Act or the CLEAR Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Federal Trade Commission to annually publish a report with certain information about its investigations of unfair or deceptive practices, including the number and disposition of such investigations.</p>]]>
        </text>
